General.Name: Ausgold Ltd
General.Description: Ausgold Limited explores for gold and other precious metals. The company's flagship property is the Katanning gold project, which covers approximately 4,000 square kilometers located in Katanning greenstone belt in south-western Western Australia. It also explores for copper, iron, nickel, chromium, and sulphide deposits. Ausgold Limited was incorporated in 2009 and is based in Perth, Australia.
